God morning, our ad was rejected but the reason that it was rejected was a mistake on Newsbreaks part. IN the headline for my add I stated "Special VIP Meet and Greet $85 Limited availability". The Add was rejected because they say the price is $65 on our flyer. That is incorrect. The VIP with Meet and Greet is $85 as listed on the flyer.
The user has uploaded an image of a promotional flyer for the East Coast Thunder event featuring Molly Hatchet, scheduled for May 24-25, 2025, with various activities and auctions.

Good morning! I'm sorry to hear about the confusion with your ad rejection. If you believe the rejection was a mistake, you can submit an appeal. Please email adsupport@newsbreak.com with the details of your ad and explain the situation. Make sure to include any relevant information or attachments, such as your flyer, to support your case.

Good morning, Phil! I'm sorry to hear about the confusion with your ad rejection. Since you mentioned that the rejection was due to a mistake on NewsBreak's part, I recommend submitting an appeal. Please email adsupport@newsbreak.com with the subject line 'Urgent: Ad Rejected - Action Required' and include details about the error along with any supporting documents, like your flyer. This will help expedite the review process and get your ad back on track. You can find more information on what to do next in this article: [My ad got rejected.
